---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Free Downloads | Estate Planning Guides & Checklists | Mesa Estate Planning"
  description="Free downloadable estate planning guides, checklists, and resources from Mesa Estate Planning. Plain-English PDFs to help Arizona families plan ahead."
  keywords="estate planning downloads, free estate planning guide, arizona probate guide, business succession checklist"
>
  <section class="services-index-hero">
    <div class="services-index-hero-content">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow" style="opacity:1;animation:none;">Resources</div>
      <h1 class="hero-h1" style="opacity:1;animation:none;">Free guides and <em>checklists</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-body" style="opacity:1;animation:none;">Downloadable PDFs on Arizona estate planning, probate, business succession, and more — written in plain English by our attorneys.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-index-grid">
    <div class="services-index-section">
      <div class="services-index-label">Coming Soon</div>
      <div class="services-card-grid">
        <div class="services-index-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span style="font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--bronze);font-weight:600;">Coming Soon</span>
          <h3>Arizona Probate Guide</h3>
          <p>A plain-English walkthrough of Arizona's probate process — what it costs, how long it takes, and how to avoid it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-index-card" style="opacity:0.65;">
          <span style="font-size:0.65rem;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--bronze);font-weight:600;">Coming Soon</span>
          <h3>Business Succession Checklist</h3>
          <p>A step-by-step checklist for business owners planning a transition — whether you're selling, passing it on, or retiring.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="services-index-cta">
      <h2>Want personalized guidance now?</h2>
      <p>These resources are coming soon. In the meantime, a free consultation is the fastest way to get answers specific to your situation.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-bronze">Book Free Consultation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
